    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring a visceral connection to the tarmac. The double-VANOS system has been recently calibrated, and the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to maintain structural rigidity under high cornering loads. While the exterior shows honest signs of use consistent with its 'good' status, the suspension geometry remains true, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for precise lateral control. A perfect candidate for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and analog performance over garage-queen aesthetics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
