    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a well-preserved luxury sedan that perfectly balances performance and elegance. Finished in a deep Obsidian Black, the paint remains vibrant and has been recently waxed, though minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips typical of careful highway use are present upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple charcoal leather upholstery and genuine wood accents; the seats remain firm and supportive, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. This vehicle is technologically current, equipped with a responsive touchscreen interface, premium surround sound, and a suite of driver-assist features, all of which function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine delivers power smoothly and shifts effortlessly, backed by a complete service history from authorized dealerships. Most recently, it passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and received a fresh set of high-performance tires and a new battery. This car has been driven with care and maintained without compromise, offering a turn-key experience for a buyer looking for a reliable, high-quality vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
